# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# backend — Variables de Entorno
# Copiar como .env. NUNCA commitear .env con valores reales.
# El backend es el único componente con credenciales de base de datos — el
# frontend nunca las ve, y ai-services nunca las necesita.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── Aplicación ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CLOUDBANK_APP_ENVIRONMENT=development
CLOUDBANK_APP_VERSION=2.0.0
CLOUDBANK_APP_LOG_LEVEL=INFO
CLOUDBANK_APP_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=["http://localhost:3000"]
CLOUDBANK_APP_ALLOWED_HOSTS=["localhost"]
CLOUDBANK_APP_MAX_PAYLOAD_SIZE=1048576

# ─── ai-services (único componente que el backend llama para IA) ─────────────
CLOUDBANK_AI_SERVICES_URL=http://localhost:8100
CLOUDBANK_AI_SERVICES_TIMEOUT_SECS=90

# ─── Redis (rate limiting, checkpoints, cache de API keys) ───────────────────
CLOUDBANK_REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379/0
CLOUDBANK_REDIS_PASSWORD=your-redis-password
CLOUDBANK_REDIS_MAX_CONNECTIONS=20
CLOUDBANK_REDIS_SOCKET_TIMEOUT=5
CLOUDBANK_REDIS_KEY_PREFIX=cloudbank:

# ─── PostgreSQL ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CLOUDBANK_DATABASE_URL=postgresql://cloudbank:change-me@localhost:5432/cloudbank
CLOUDBANK_DATABASE_POOL_MIN_SIZE=5
CLOUDBANK_DATABASE_POOL_MAX_SIZE=20
CLOUDBANK_DATABASE_COMMAND_TIMEOUT=30
CLOUDBANK_DATABASE_SSL_MODE=prefer

# ─── Seguridad ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# encryption_key: 32 bytes exactos, generar con: python -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_hex(16))"
CLOUDBANK_SECURITY_ENCRYPTION_KEY=change-me-32-chars-exactly!!!!
CLOUDBANK_SECURITY_VAULT_URL=http://vault:8200
CLOUDBANK_SECURITY_VAULT_TOKEN=your-vault-token
CLOUDBANK_SECURITY_JWT_SECRET=change-me-jwt-secret-256-bits
CLOUDBANK_SECURITY_JWT_EXPIRY_MINUTES=60
CLOUDBANK_SECURITY_RATE_LIMIT_DEFAULT_RPM=60
CLOUDBANK_SECURITY_RATE_LIMIT_EVALUATE_RPM=10
CLOUDBANK_SECURITY_MAX_PAYLOAD_BYTES=1048576

# ─── Login demo del frontend (Fase 1 académica — ver docs/FREE_TIER_ARCHITECTURE.md §11) ──
CLOUDBANK_SECURITY_DEMO_OFFICER_USERNAME=officer
# Generar con: python -c "from passlib.context import CryptContext; print(CryptContext(schemes=['bcrypt']).hash('tu-password'))"
CLOUDBANK_SECURITY_DEMO_OFFICER_PASSWORD_HASH=
CLOUDBANK_SECURITY_DEMO_OFFICER_ROLE=risk_officer

# ─── Observabilidad ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CLOUDBANK_OBS_OTLP_ENDPOINT=http://jaeger:4317
CLOUDBANK_OBS_SERVICE_NAME=cloudbank-backend
CLOUDBANK_OBS_SAMPLE_RATE=1.0
CLOUDBANK_OBS_METRICS_ENABLED=true
CLOUDBANK_OBS_TRACING_ENABLED=true
